{"tid":2315451,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"[12月07號]美國大選新聞總匯","createTime":"2020-12-07T07:56:28.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-08T08:22:12.000Z","uid":54550,"like":95,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":75,"replies":[{"pid":"f0de101a4de52738de1554b3a7ac3239a6ce6ad0","tid":2315451,"uid":54550,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-07T07:56:28.000Z","msg":"寫在前面：<br />\nFake News定義 - 扭曲事實報導嘅新聞、作出嚟嘅新聞就係Fake News<br />\n<strong>但係</strong>一啲仍然發展緊嘅事、當未verify需要繼續追查嘅嘢唔係Fake news<br />\n<br />\n而家第四權完全失效，所有有信譽嘅左翼媒體全部淪為Propaganda，向呢個時候我地要得到真相好困難。19有個建議個人覺得幾好，我地可以從發言人嘅身份去判斷呢個消息可信任與否<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span class=\"red\">意圖向個帖入面貼leftwing media嗰堆友唔該自動消失</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n大家好又到左星期一 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong>Michigan</strong><br />\n<br />\n汁 - <a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=yql-mpgNY2U\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3Dyql-mpgNY2U&d=MiI%2Ba6G9rqdq%2F0stJtUYTnO0ZW31AiaZ%2BXmqixBX3cM%3D&h=9469e9e9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=yql-mpgNY2U</a><br />\nJenna Ellis直接接受Fox訪問<br />\n<br />\nMI嘅官畀侵嘅律師團檢查22部Dominion投票機.  畀佢地&quot;forensic audit&quot; 驗屍咁驗 <br />\n<br />\n汁 - <a href=\"https://www.migop.org/benson_demands_data_deleted?recruiter_id=660242\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.migop.org%2Fbenson_demands_data_deleted%3Frecruiter_id%3D660242&d=MiI%2Ba6G9rqdq%2F0stJtUYTnO0ZW31AiaZ%2BXmqixBX3cM%3D&h=51ec979a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.migop.org/benson_demands_data_deleted?recruiter_id=660242</a><br />\nMI嘅GOP官網<br />\n<br />\nMI共和黨人於上週五發言 當MI嘅共和黨要求全面Audit十一月選舉結果嗰陣MI州務卿試圖刪除選舉數據以迴避審計選票 喺County嘅文員memo顯示 州務卿 Jocelyn Benson叫堆文員刪除電子投票名冊及相關嘅文件 包括其中一個爭議郡 Wayne County<br />\n<br />\n<strong>Arizona </strong><br />\n<br />\nRT者 - Solomon Yue<br />\n汁 - <a href=\"https://theconservativetreehouse.com/2020/12/06/report-fbi-raided-maricopia-county-residence-to-retrieve-evidence-of-cyber-intrusion-into-voting-systems/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftheconservativetreehouse.com%2F2020%2F12%2F06%2Freport-fbi-raided-maricopia-county-residence-to-retrieve-evidence-of-cyber-intrusion-into-voting-systems%2F&d=MiI%2Ba6G9rqdq%2F0stJtUYTnO0ZW31AiaZ%2BXmqixBX3cM%3D&h=1c18d7cc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://theconservativetreehouse.com/2020/12/06/report-fbi-raided-maricopia-county-residence-to-retrieve-evidence-of-cyber-intrusion-into-voting-systems/</a><br />\n<br />\n呢個汁引述係Forbes報導 <br />\n<a href=\"https://www.forbes.com/sites/thomasbrewster/2020/12/04/exclusive-the-fbi-is-investigating-voter-data-theft-in-this-key-2020-election-battleground/?sh=37b5dc9a34a4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.forbes.com%2Fsites%2Fthomasbrewster%2F2020%2F12%2F04%2Fexclusive-the-fbi-is-investigating-voter-data-theft-in-this-key-2020-election-battleground%2F%3Fsh%3D37b5dc9a34a4&d=MiI%2Ba6G9rqdq%2F0stJtUYTnO0ZW31AiaZ%2BXmqixBX3cM%3D&h=b653b67f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.forbes.com/sites/thomasbrewster/2020/12/04/exclusive-the-fbi-is-investigating-voter-data-theft-in-this-key-2020-election-battleground/?sh=37b5dc9a34a4</a><br />\nForbes原報導重點 <br />\nFBI原來早於11月5號突襲Maricopa County入面嘅一間屋 沒收左電腦、硬碟, USB, 及一堆懷疑與選舉系統有關嘅電子設備 而Forbes就喺一個月之後發現左佢地行動嘅手令 ，Forbes接觸過AZ嘅Justice Dept，AZ嘅Justice Dept對呢個行動不作評價 ，Forbes嘅記者有再嘗試接觸過懷疑與是次行動相關嘅事主 但係佢地無辦法搵到佢<br />\n<br />\n而引述Forbes嘅汁嘅此篇文章，作者係行文中流露對FBI嘅行動充滿焦慮 因為佢地過去呢一個月嘅表現不如理想 而且亦有隱藏Hunter Biden隻hard disc嘅前科 <br />\n<br />\n<strong>PA</strong><br />\n<br />\nRT者 - Solomon Yue <br />\n汁 - <a href=\"https://www.ntd.com/justice-alito-moves-up-supreme-court-deadline-in-key-pennsylvania-mail-in-ballot-case_536812.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ntd.com%2Fjustice-alito-moves-up-supreme-court-deadline-in-key-pennsylvania-mail-in-ballot-case_536812.html&d=MiI%2Ba6G9rqdq%2F0stJtUYTnO0ZW31AiaZ%2BXmqixBX3cM%3D&h=2532d18d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.ntd.com/justice-alito-moves-up-supreme-court-deadline-in-key-pennsylvania-mail-in-ballot-case_536812.html</a><br />\n<br />\n關於PA嘅GOP人對Act 77違憲嘅訴訟 <br />\nSupreme Court法官Alito將呢件案排前啲審 此案將於12月8號開審<br />\n而據Solomon Yue嘅Twitter引述 呢單案將會由Clarence Thomas 主理 <br />\n<br />\n汁 - PA州長自己個Twitter<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/GovernorTomWolf/status/1334857800103714818\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FGovernorTomWolf%2Fstatus%2F1334857800103714818&d=MiI%2Ba6G9rqdq%2F0stJtUYTnO0ZW31AiaZ%2BXmqixBX3cM%3D&h=eccd9ed6\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FGovernorTomWolf%2Fstatus%2F1334857800103714818&h=b47717b4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/GovernorTomWolf/status/1334857800103714818</a><br />\n<br />\n有堆PA嘅律師要求州長民主黨Tom Wolf就PA選舉一事出席特別會議 <br />\n州長回應呢個要求 話攞嚟搞. PA有好公平公正嘅選舉. 侵團隊應該係時候move on<br />\n<br />\n<strong>保持五秒距離新聞</strong><br />\n<br />\nRT者Solomon Yue<br />\n汁 - <a href=\"https://www.thegatewaypundit.com/2020/12/china-whistleblower-steps-forward-reveals-video-photos-alleged-chinese-counterfeit-ballot-printing-operations-us-ballots-mi-fl-nc/?utm_source=Twitter&amp;utm_campaign=websitesharingbuttons\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thegatewaypundit.com%2F2020%2F12%2Fchina-whistleblower-steps-forward-reveals-video-photos-alleged-chinese-counterfeit-ballot-printing-operations-us-ballots-mi-fl-nc%2F%3Futm_source%3DTwitter%26utm_campaign%3Dwebsitesharingbuttons&d=MiI%2Ba6G9rqdq%2F0stJtUYTnO0ZW31AiaZ%2BXmqixBX3cM%3D&h=d7b9624d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.thegatewaypundit.com/2020/12/china-whistleblower-steps-forward-reveals-video-photos-alleged-chinese-counterfeit-ballot-printing-operations-us-ballots-mi-fl-nc/?utm_source=Twitter&amp;utm_campaign=websitesharingbuttons</a><br />\n<br />\n有來自中國嘅Whistleblowers透露啲廣東嘅工廠印制大量美國大選空白選票 牽涉嘅州份有MI, FL (Florida), NC ( North Carolina) <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n其他關於大選嘅新聞若無相對可信嘅RT者唔會喺呢度詳述 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n***<br />\n[12月04號]美國大選新聞總匯<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/2311533/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/2311533/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n[12月03號]美國大選新聞總匯<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/2310358/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/2310358/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n[12月02號]美國大選新聞總匯<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/2309141/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/2309141/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n[12月01號]美國大選新聞總匯<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/2307562/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/2307562/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n[11月30號]美國大選新聞總匯<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/2306083/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/2306083/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n[11月27號]美國大選新聞總匯<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/2302599/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/2302599/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n[11月26號]美國大選新聞總匯<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/2301284/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/2301284/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n[11月25號]美國大選新聞總匯<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/2299862/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/2299862/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n[11月24號]美國大選新聞總匯<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/2298532/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/2298532/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n[11月23號]美國大選新聞總匯<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/2297112/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/2297112/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n[11月20號]美國大選新聞總匯<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/2293239/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/2293239/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n[11月19號]美國大選新聞總匯<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/2291882/page/1\" d